dress appropriately.

19:49.981 --> 19:51.358
The fuck is this?

19:51.399 --> 19:53.026
What does it fucking look like,
boyfriend?

19:53.068 --> 19:55.487
Freak show
is what it looks like.

19:55.528 --> 19:57.739
How am I supposed
to dress appropriately?

19:57.781 --> 20:00.700
I'm a woman. I don't have
any goddamn boy clothes.

20:00.742 --> 20:02.369
JORDAN: Hey. Hey.

20:02.410 --> 20:06.831
Don't worry about it. OK?
We'll get you some clothes.

20:06.873 --> 20:11.586
-Can anybody spare some clothes?
-Not my vintage stuff, but sure.

20:37.612 --> 20:41.032
I'm not sure
that entirely suits you, Jordan.

20:41.991 --> 20:43.451
Not my color?

20:45.328 --> 20:48.748
OK. I'd like you all
to say hello to Alexander,

20:48.790 --> 20:52.293
who is obviously dealing
with some complicated issues.

20:52.335 --> 20:55.839
We welcome him gladly
and with love.

20:57.298 --> 20:59.551
OK, let's have some fun.

20:59.592 --> 21:02.887
