1:28:03.658 --> 1:28:07.328
Come on.
All right, stay close to me.

1:28:13.251 --> 1:28:15.837
You guys go to the infirmary.
Stay there. Don't leave.

1:28:15.879 --> 1:28:17.714
I'm gonna get
that damn generator working,

1:28:17.756 --> 1:28:20.008
and I don't trust Owen and Cora.

1:28:23.386 --> 1:28:25.138
You go ahead.
I'm gonna go get the rifles.

1:28:25.180 --> 1:28:27.599
-No!
-This isn't over.

1:28:27.640 --> 1:28:29.351
You know that, right?

1:28:29.392 --> 1:28:31.811
You go on ahead.
I'll be right behind you.

1:28:31.853 --> 1:28:33.688
Do either of you
know how to shoot?

1:28:33.730 --> 1:28:35.482
BOTH: Yes.

1:28:35.523 --> 1:28:37.484
Of course you do.

1:29:12.769 --> 1:29:15.522
OWEN: Cora!
Where are the goddamn rifles?

1:29:17.315 --> 1:29:18.900
Cora!

1:29:46.219 --> 1:29:47.887
(OWEN GRUNTS)

1:30:19.919 --> 1:30:22.088
You don't remember me, do you?

1:30:23.840 --> 1:30:25.467
So many kids
have been through here,

1:30:25.508 --> 1:30:28.762
how can you be expected
to remember them all?

1:30:28.803 --> 1:30:31.806
-Molly, I...
-Oh, no. I'm not Molly.

1:30:32.766 --> 1:30:35.060
Molly's dead in her car
on the way here,

1:30:35.101 --> 1:30:36.811
so I could take her place.

1:30:38.646 --> 1:30:40.648
My name's Angie.

1:30:41.733 --> 1:30:44.903
Angie Phelps.
Do you remember her?

1:30:45.862 --> 1:30:46.988
Stay down!

1:30:50.200 --> 1:30:53.870
No? Angie Phelps. Nothing?

1:30:55.705 --> 1:31:00.543
She was only 14...
when you first met her.

1:31:01.836 --> 1:31:05.674
She was a good girl... then.

1:31:07.509 --> 1:31:10.970
Before all this,
before you put her in that chair

1:31:11.012 --> 1:31:15.475
and burned
all the good out of her.

1:31:15.517 --> 1:31:18.019
-You must understand...
-No, I mustn't.

1:31:18.061 --> 1:31:21.314
No more words,
Owen. No more speeches!

1:31:21.356 --> 1:31:24.984
When Angie left here,
it was the suicide attempts,

1:31:25.026 --> 1:31:29.364
and the loneliness,
and the self-hatred,

1:31:29.406 --> 1:31:35.704
and pills, and the doctors, and,
oh, the anger, so much anger.

1:31:37.122 --> 1:31:41.209
I woke up one morning
and realized...

1:31:42.711 --> 1:31:45.213
my soul was just hollow.

1:31:47.257 --> 1:31:49.759
But you know all about that.

1:31:51.886 --> 1:31:54.556
That's what you do to people.

1:31:55.598 --> 1:31:57.225
To children.

1:31:58.226 --> 1:32:00.895
You hollow them out.

1:32:05.233 --> 1:32:07.652
And when all of this comes out,

1:32:08.737 --> 1:32:11.197
in the news, on TV,

1:32:11.239 --> 1:32:14.826
all of the bodies,
all the horror of it,

1:32:14.868 --> 1:32:21.082
no one will ever send their kids
to a place like this again.

1:32:22.542 --> 1:32:26.504
And you, and everyone like you,

1:32:26.546 --> 1:32:32.927
will be burning in hell
right next to me.

1:32:35.388 --> 1:32:36.848
(STRAINS)

1:32:40.310 --> 1:32:42.020
Stop.

1:32:43.271 --> 1:32:45.523
Get off her.

1:32:45.565 --> 1:32:48.610
(CHOKING)

1:32:55.283 --> 1:32:57.202
Easy now, buddy.

1:33:02.415 --> 1:33:04.167
You know what to do, Jordan.

1:33:06.169 --> 1:33:07.295
Do it!

1:33:09.964 --> 1:33:12.884
Shooting a sick, old dog
is one thing, Jordan.

1:33:13.635 --> 1:33:16.388
But shooting a man...

1:33:16.429 --> 1:33:21.893
No, sir. I mean, that takes
a certain kind of heart.

1:33:22.644 --> 1:33:25.105
You don't know me.

1:33:25.146 --> 1:33:27.273
You don't know
anything about me.

1:33:27.315 --> 1:33:31.736
Oh, I know everything about you.
I know you're scared.

1:33:32.821 --> 1:33:35.615
I know you want this to end.

1:33:35.657 --> 1:33:38.243
But not like this, son.
Not like this.

1:33:38.993 --> 1:33:41.121
Jordan, you saw the pictures.

1:33:41.162 --> 1:33:43.623
All those kids.
All that torture.

1:33:43.665 --> 1:33:46.167
You know what he does here.

1:33:46.209 --> 1:33:50.714
End this now! You're strong
enough to do this, Jordan.

1:34:04.602 --> 1:34:06.229
No.

1:34:08.314 --> 1:34:10.650
I'm strong enough

1:34:10.692 --> 1:34:13.862
to not do this.

1:34:19.325 --> 1:34:22.037
(YELLS)

1:34:26.082 --> 1:34:28.460
(GROANS)

1:34:31.629 --> 1:34:37.385
All I did was make those kids
into who they wanted to be.

1:34:38.928 --> 1:34:43.641
You made me too.
And this is my truth.

1:34:43.683 --> 1:34:46.686
Respect. Renew.

1:34:46.728 --> 1:34:49.898
Rejoice. Revenge!

1:35:07.082 --> 1:35:11.252
It gets easier. You'll see.

1:35:12.796 --> 1:35:15.382
There are so many
camps like this.

1:35:15.423 --> 1:35:17.425
We can cleanse them all.

1:35:19.678 --> 1:35:22.764
(DISTANT POLICE SIREN)

1:35:26.017 --> 1:35:27.977
OK.

1:35:28.019 --> 1:35:31.231
So, what are we gonna tell them?
We can say he... did it.

1:35:31.272 --> 1:35:33.274
-He killed them and we...
-Enough.

1:35:35.694 --> 1:35:38.113
No more lies.

1:35:40.490 --> 1:35:42.200
Where does it end?

1:35:42.242 --> 1:35:46.663
When every camp
like this is closed.

1:35:46.705 --> 1:35:48.957
When we've killed them all.

1:35:50.250 --> 1:35:53.837
We could do that, Jordan.
You and me.

1:35:59.009 --> 1:36:01.344
You can try to stop me,

1:36:01.386 --> 1:36:06.141
but I'm going to go
to my friends now.

1:36:07.350 --> 1:36:11.813
We're gonna leave this place
and never look back.

1:36:11.855 --> 1:36:17.485
And no one is ever going to
tell us who we are ever again.

1:36:18.319 --> 1:36:21.948
Not him. Not you.

1:36:23.533 --> 1:36:25.368
No one.

1:36:28.705 --> 1:36:30.957
I'm trying to save you.

1:36:35.837 --> 1:36:38.006
No one needs to save me.

1:37:30.141 --> 1:37:33.228
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

1:37:39.567 --> 1:37:42.696
-Can I go?
-Are you family?

1:37:42.737 --> 1:37:44.489
Yeah. He is.

1:38:26.906 --> 1:38:28.450
So,

1:38:28.491 --> 1:38:32.203
back to the real world now,
I guess.

1:38:32.245 --> 1:38:34.622
What are you gonna tell
your parents?

1:38:37.208 --> 1:38:39.127
We'll tell them together.

1:38:49.137 --> 1:38:51.139
What about you?

1:38:55.518 --> 1:38:57.228
Get emancipated.

1:39:02.984 --> 1:39:04.986
Live my life.

1:39:08.615 --> 1:39:11.368
You live your best life.

1:39:13.661 --> 1:39:15.246
Always.

1:39:16.373 --> 1:39:20.001
(CHUCKLES)

1:39:38.311 --> 1:39:42.732
(* "FUCKIN' PERFECT" BY PINK)

1:40:01.042 --> 1:40:03.670
Subtitles: IYUNO-SDI GROUP
